## Next Steps for Deployment

To complete the Analytics setup:

1. **Enable Analytics in Vercel Dashboard**
   - Navigate to your project in Vercel dashboard
   - Go to Analytics section in sidebar
   - Click "Enable" button

2. **Deploy to Vercel**
   ```bash
   vercel deploy
   ```

3. **Verify Analytics**
   - Visit your deployed site
   - Open browser DevTools > Network tab
   - Look for XHR/Fetch requests to `/<unique-path>/view`
   - Check Vercel dashboard for analytics data

## Technical Notes

- The Analytics component is a client-side component that automatically tracks page views
- No additional configuration needed for basic page view tracking
- Analytics data will only appear after deployment to Vercel
- The component works seamlessly with Next.js App Router navigation
- No impact on build size or performance (lazy loaded)

